&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. 于地区选择及通知确定后&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung1-272x580.png" alt="" width="272" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung1-272x580.png 272w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung1.png 422w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 272px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
