&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4.输入认可学校电邮地址&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__3-265x580.jpg" alt="" width="265" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__3-265x580.jpg 265w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__3.jpg 412w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 265px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
