&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__4-266x580.jpg" alt="" width="266" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__4-266x580.jpg 266w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung__4.jpg 413w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 266px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
