&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1321041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/samsung5.jpg 356w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7. 成功登入教育商店&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1321046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025081255650-581x580.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025081255650-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025081255650.jpg 902w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025081255650-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 581px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
